snippet.title: Borrowhelen Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2116080/Borrowhelen

Borrowhelen is a 90s-style first-person shooter set in a fantastical realm like no other. As the brilliant scientist Ordin Gilbellt, you dive into battle against cultists and mythical creatures, wielding powerful and unique weapons.

Website: https://www.artoflaskow.com/borrowhelen
Twitter (X): https://x.com/Laskow0o
